MedTrack – AI Powered Healthcare Management System using Flask and AWS

1. Project Overview
MedTrack is a cloud-enabled healthcare management system designed to connect patients and doctors through a simple digital platform. The system allows patients to register, book appointments with doctors, view diagnosis reports, and maintain their medical history. Doctors can manage appointments, provide diagnoses, and track patient records through a centralized dashboard.
The system also includes an AI Health Assistant that analyzes daily health data such as sleep, mood, stress level, water intake, and activity level to generate a health score and personalized recommendations.
The platform is built using Flask for backend development, HTML/CSS for frontend interfaces, and JSON-based storage for managing application data.
Key Features
• Secure patient and doctor registration and login
• Appointment booking system
• Doctor dashboard for managing patients and diagnoses
• Patient dashboard for viewing medical history
• AI-based health assistant for wellness analysis
• Cloud deployment capability using AWS
