 2.4 AI Health Assistant
The AI Health Assistant evaluates daily health inputs provided by the user such as:
• Sleep hours
• Stress level
• Mood level
• Water intake
• Physical activity (steps)
• Screen time
• Junk food intake
Based on these inputs, the system calculates a health score and generates a summary along with personalized health recommendations.
